title: IBASE announces 3.5” SBC with 13th Gen Intel Core CPUs
description: IBASE Technology has introduced a 3.5″ Single Board Computer equipped with 13th Gen Intel Core processors which utilize a performance hybrid architecture, integrating up to 6 Performance-cores (P-core) and 8 Efficient-cores (E-core), optimizing the SBC for handling demanding computing tasks.
